  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779180/extras/336aba6a433dd6367d40bce68ee28f2c.avif?t=1643317706\" width=600 height=353 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779180/extras/1860cbfb2fc8ef5ba37c63fb083fd50d.avif?t=1643317706\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>Knight's Try is a difficult 64 bit styled platforming game. Take on the role of an honorable Knight of Trye attempting to complete their sacred trial by leaping through a world full of perilous pitfalls and dangerous traps!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779180/extras/ae01db40dee832cd28b879681153a9c9.avif?t=1643317706\" width=600 height=600 /></span><br><br><u>FEATURES:</u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Classic platforming action!<br></li><li> Nostalgic 64 bit 3D graphics!!<br></li><li> Adjustable difficulty level!!!<br></li><li> Custom soundtrack powered by your own MIDI files!!!!<br></li><li> Knights!!!!!</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779180/extras/bf99bcf889df2dc1923bca97e2855dfd.avif?t=1643317706\" width=732 height=780 /></span><br><br>If at first you don't succeed, try Trye again!",
